{"tid":2025500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王婆婆： 被禁離開深圳超過九個月 我十分想念香港","createTime":"2020-05-20T09:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T16:14:56.000Z","uid":125168,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"38b7cedd1d752273fc9cf736bb8a7e1db1b2cf7a","tid":2025500,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JqLJFZZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJqLJFZZ.jpg&h=10e2d4a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n王婆婆被禁離開深圳超過九個月 「我十分想念香港」<br />\n立場報道  <a href=\"https://is.gd/MqTbfk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FMqTbfk&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=e92bf464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/MqTbfk</a><br />\n<br />\n// 您好！！！非常高興收到你的電郵！<br />\n因為被禁離開深圳已經超過九個月，現在身體及精神均是有生以來最差。我十分想念香港!!!<br />\n祝閣下一切安好!!! 加油！！！<br />\nAlexandra //<br />\n#王婆婆 #狗共 #籠的傳人 #扼殺自由"},{"pid":"83c2fb4fe482750913b3a9a0d1b675f73433fdd5","tid":2025500,"uid":220451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:34:47.000Z","msg":"王婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d63eb0bcbb3e6db3ad806e7e9993c31cae7e4f6","tid":2025500,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69dccf6b7a2d9552ad9adb093d480fd3669113c0","tid":2025500,"uid":125168,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:34:55.000Z","msg":"王婆婆自去年 8 月 11 日在太古地鐵站被帶走後不知所蹤。她後來經電郵向本網透露，自己在 8 月 14 日於深圳被捕，被送入福田看守所，罪名是「尋釁滋事」，再於 8 月 30 日被轉到深圳市第三看守所，9 月 29 日獲保釋離開，其後需接受五日的「愛國教育」。<br />\n<br />\n完美例子解